name: Lightlife
0:
”Alexa, launch Light Life.”
”Tell me the Light Life for January 1st, 1970.”
”Give me the Light Life for is June 19th, 2003.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: light life
des: Ever wonder how far light has traveled since a certain date? Light life reports the distance light has travelled from the sun since a certain date. Be amazed at how far photons have traveled. Light life also reports how many seconds have elapsed since the provided date.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
